c: 2
v: 164
t: "Inene ekudalweni kwamazulu nomhlaba, nasekuguqulweni kobusuku bube yimini, neenqanawa ezihamba, zinqumle iilwandle ziqulethe oko kubalulekileyo eluntwini, namanzi (emvula) uAllâh Awathumela phantsi esuka esibhakabhakeni, Avuselele umhlaba ngawo emva kokuba ubufile nezidalwa ezinyakazelayo zeendidi zonke Azithe saa (emhlabeni) nasekuvuthuzenikomoyanamafuaphakathikwesibhakabhaka nomhlaba, (konke oko) kuyimiqondiso kubantu ukuba baqiqe"